{[#]} {[%tqu "En","White to move.","","","e4e5","Very important to play it before including 00-00. Why? Because Black will have the f7 pawn problem.",10]} 8. e5 $1 {Very important to play it before including 00-00. Why? Because Black will have the f7 pawn problem.} (8. O-O $6 {After the inclusion of 00-00, Black's position is not so bad.} O-O 9. e5 Nd5 10. Qb3 Nf4 $1 $15 {[%csl Gf7][%cal Gf8f7] The knight will go to g6 or e6. Black's position is already slightly better, and all this is possible because the f7 pawn is defended.}) 8... Nd5 9. Qb3 $1 {[%csl Rf7][%cal Gc4f7] Black cannot move the knight because the f7 pawn is hanging.} c6 10. O-O O-O 11. Nxd4 $14 *

