{[#]} {[%tqu "En","White to move.","","","c1g5","My recommendation. The most interesting move.",10,"c4b5","Most common, but I don't like it, because of Qd5!",0]} 10. Bg5 {My recommendation. The most interesting move.} (10. Bb5 {Most common, but I don't like it, because of Qd5!} Qd5 $1 11. Nbxd4 O-O 12. Bxc6 bxc6 13. Qc2 c5 $132 {I feel that this is not a position for a long game, and Black can concretely equalize in more than one way.}) 10... Be7 11. Bxe7 Qxe7 {The correct recapture.} 12. Bb5 $36 {[%cal Rd8d5] Black doesn't have Bb5.} *

